Cruising California: A road trip guide to the Golden State's urban gems
From the bustling energy of San Francisco to the laid-back beach vibes of San Diego, California is home to some of the most diverse and vibrant urban cities in the United States. Discover many iconic experiences and landmarks, like the Golden Gate Bridge, Hollywood Sign, and the San Diego Zoo. A road trip allows you to stop and take in these famous sights at your own pace.
